        <p class="gallery-caption">Landing page &amp; Detail page wireframes &amp; designs for the Currents redesign.</p>
        <section class="article_content article_content--bottom">
            <p>To compliment this new landing page, we also helped redesign the Currents’ shared “Detail Page” developing a solution that would allow for anything from a short video writeup to a data-visualization deep-dive to be the editorial focus, while also helping to promote longer page-views and context-setting in-page story-to-story way finding, allowing an end-user to see the bigger picture and understand the shared themes across stories.</p>
            <p>The end product was <a href="https://www.kauffman.org/currents">The Kauffman Foundation’s Currents Landing page</a> which helped organized the wide variety of content being centrally published into one cohesive page that could be used to thematically group “Featured Story Cards” or allow the end-user to quickly browse content by topics.</p>
        </section>
